# Fork of VbaGit to TRY to bring this wonderful feature to Microsoft Word

No promises, but I will try. I really need this to work, as I write quite a lot of VBA in Word. It's a mess trying to keep things in order. Hope, hope.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
